'''Odve'starn''' was a city on the [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] of [[Bothawui/Legends|Bothawui]]. It was located on the western shores of the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] western continent, facing the [[Rhyde'vak]] [[Ocean/Legends|ocean]]. [[Kolme'starn]] was found to the east.

